.Sh NAME
.Nm sndwave-play
.Nd play a sound file
.Sh SYNOPSIS
.Nm sndwave-play
.Ar
.Sh DESCRIPTION
.Nm
plays one or more sound files on various operating systems using standard audio
output APIs. The following table summarizes which audio API is used where:
.Pp
.Bl -tag -width MacOSX10XXX -compact
.It Linux
ALSA or OSS
.It OpenBSD
sndio
.It FreeBSD
/dev/dsp (OSS)
.It Solaris
/dev/audio
.It MacOSX 10.6
CoreAudio
.It MacOSX 10.7
AudioToolbox
.It Win32
waveOut
.El
